							  </svg>
							</span>
						</button>
					</div>
					-->
				</div>
			</div>
			<!-- End Collapse -->
			</nav>
		</header>
		<!-- ========== END HEADER ========== -->

		<!-- ========== MAIN CONTENT ========== -->
		<main id="content">
		<!-- Hero -->
		<div>
			<div class="w-full bg-center bg-cover"
			  style="background-image: url(https://images.pexels.com/photos/268261/pexels-photo-268261.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=2);">
			  <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-full h-full bg-gray-900 bg-opacity-50 py-12">
				<div class="text-center">
				  <div class="container px-4 mx-auto">
						<div class="max-w-[85rem] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-24 space-y-8">
					
						<!-- Title -->
						<div class="max-w-3xl text-center mx-auto">
							<h1 class="block font-medium text-gray-200 text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl">
							our mission
							</h1>
						</div>
						<!-- End Title -->
					
						<div class="max-w-3xl text-center mx-auto">
							<p class="text-lg text-white/90">who we are, why we exist, and what we do</p>
						</div>
					
						</div>
				  </div>
				</div>
			  </div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<!-- End Hero -->

			<!-- Clients -->
			<div class="px-4 lg:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="relative py-6 md:py-10 overflow-hidden border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-neutral-700 before:absolute before:top-0 before:start-0 before:z-10 before:w-20 before:h-full before:bg-gradient-to-r before:from-white before:to-transparent after:absolute after:top-0 after:end-0 after:w-20 after:h-full after:bg-gradient-to-l after:from-white after:to-transparent dark:before:from-neutral-900 dark:after:from-neutral-900">
				<div class="flex justify-between items-center gap-x-4">

					<img class="w-7 md:w-10 h-auto text-black mx-auto dark:text-white" src="/src/assets/images/carousel-1.png" alt="Rabbit iconography, attributed to Freepik on Flaticon">
					<img class="w-7 md:w-10 h-auto text-black mx-auto dark:text-white" src="/src/assets/images/carousel-2.png" alt="Rabbit iconography, attributed to Freepik on Flaticon">
					<img class="w-7 md:w-10 h-auto text-black mx-auto dark:text-white" src="/src/assets/images/carousel-3.png" alt="Rabbit iconography, attributed to nandaraihan on Flaticon">

				</div>
			</div>
			</div>
			<!-- End Clients -->

			<!-- Icon Blocks -->
			<div class="max-w-[85rem] px-4 py-10 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 lg:py-14 mx-auto">
				<div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
				<!-- Grid -->
				<div class="grid gap-12">
					<div>
					<h2 class="text-3xl text-gray-800 font-bold lg:text-4xl dark:text-white">
						in a nutshell
					</h2>
					<p class="mt-3 text-gray-800 dark:text-neutral-400">
						We seek to reduce the number of rabbits that are abandoned or rehomed due to behavioral issues stemming from being isolated from others. Rabbits are meant to be in bonded pairs or family units; because of this, making sure they're bonded greatly supports their mental and physical health.
					</p>
					</div>
			
					<div class="space-y-6 lg:space-y-10">
					<!-- Icon Block -->
					<div class="flex gap-x-5 sm:gap-x-8">
						<svg class="shrink-0 mt-2 size-6 text-gray-800 dark:text-white" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-rabbit"><path d="M13 16a3 3 0 0 1 2.24 5"/><path d="M18 12h.01"/><path d="M18 21h-8a4 4 0 0 1-4-4 7 7 0 0 1 7-7h.2L9.6 6.4a1 1 0 1 1 2.8-2.8L15.8 7h.2c3.3 0 6 2.7 6 6v1a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-1a3 3 0 0 0-3 3"/><path d="M20 8.54V4a2 2 0 1 0-4 0v3"/><path d="M7.612 12.524a3 3 0 1 0-1.6 4.3"/></svg>						
						<div class="grow">
						<h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-neutral-200">
							who we are
						</h3>
						<p class="mt-1 text-gray-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
							We're a 501(c)(3) status pending nonprofit & rabbit rescue established in 2024, operating in Southern California with plans to expand across the United States.
						</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<!-- End Icon Block -->
			
					<!-- Icon Block -->
					<div class="flex gap-x-5 sm:gap-x-8">
						<svg class="shrink-0 mt-2 size-6 text-gray-800 dark:text-white" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-heart"><path d="M19 14c1.49-1.46 3-3.21 3-5.5A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 16.5 3c-1.76 0-3 .5-4.5 2-1.5-1.5-2.74-2-4.5-2A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 2 8.5c0 2.3 1.5 4.05 3 5.5l7 7Z"/></svg>
						<div class="grow">
						<h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-neutral-200">
							why we exist
						</h3>
						<p class="mt-1 text-gray-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
							Rabbits are subject to incredibly high levels of overpopulation and overcrowding at shelters due to a lack of proper knowledge & care to ensure they don't multiply. This is contributed to by neglectful practices from breeders and pet stores. As a result, rabbits face high euthanasia and abandonment rates and often don't survive.</br></br>
							Our goal is to turn this situation around, providing awareness, resources, and education. We do this while rescuing, rehabilitating, and finding furever homes for as many as we can.
						</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<!-- End Icon Block -->
			
					<!-- Icon Block -->
					<div class="flex gap-x-5 sm:gap-x-8">
						<svg class="shrink-0 mt-2 size-6 text-gray-800 dark:text-white" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-earth"><path d="M21.54 15H17a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v4.54"/><path d="M7 3.34V5a3 3 0 0 0 3 3a2 2 0 0 1 2 2c0 1.1.9 2 2 2a2 2 0 0 0 2-2c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h3.17"/><path d="M11 21.95V18a2 2 0 0 0-2-2a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-1a2 2 0 0 0-2-2H2.05"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/></svg>						
						<div class="grow">
						<h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-neutral-200">
							what we do
						</h3>
						<p class="mt-1 text-gray-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
							We seek to <b>provide resources to other rescues and rescuers</b>, <b>educate & promote awareness of proper animal care</b>, and <b>pull animals from shelters or dangerous situations to ensure they get a second chance at life.</b>
						</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<!-- End Icon Block -->
					</div>
				</div>
				<!-- End Grid -->
				</div>
			</div>
			<!-- End Icon Blocks -->

		</main>
		<!-- ========== END MAIN CONTENT ========== -->

		<!-- ========== FOOTER ========== -->
		<footer class="mt-auto border-t md:border-t-0 border-gray-200 dark:border-neutral-700">
			<div class="w-full max-w-7xl py-10 md:pt-0 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 mx-auto">
			<!-- Grid -->
			<div class="grid">
				<!-- Social Brands -->
				<div class="text-center md:text-end space-x-2">
				<a class="size-8 inline-flex justify-center items-center gap-x-2 text-sm font-semibold rounded-full border border-transparent text-black hover:text-gray-600 disabled:opacity-50 disabled:pointer-events-none dark:text-white dark:hover:text-neutral-400" href="https://linktr.ee/2rabbitrescue">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="flex-shrink-0 size-5"><path d="M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71"/><path d="M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71"/></svg>
				</a>
				<a class="size-8 inline-flex justify-center items-center gap-x-2 text-sm font-semibold rounded-full border border-transparent text-black hover:text-gray-600 disabled:opacity-50 disabled:pointer-events-none dark:text-white dark:hover:text-neutral-400" href="https://www.instagram.com/2rabbitrescue">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="flex-shrink-0 size-5"><rect width="20" height="20" x="2" y="2" rx="5" ry="5"/><path d="M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37z"/><line x1="17.5" x2="17.51" y1="6.5" y2="6.5"/></svg>
				</a>
				<a class="size-8 inline-flex justify-center items-center gap-x-2 text-sm font-semibold rounded-full border border-transparent text-black hover:text-gray-600 disabled:opacity-50 disabled:pointer-events-none dark:text-white dark:hover:text-neutral-400" href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/two-rabbit-rescue/">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="flex-shrink-0 size-5"><path d="M16 8a6 6 0 0 1 6 6v7h-4v-7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2 2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7h-4v-7a6 6 0 0 1 6-6z"/><rect width="4" height="12" x="2" y="9"/><circle cx="4" cy="4" r="2"/></svg>
				</a>
				<a class="size-8 inline-flex justify-center items-center gap-x-2 text-sm font-semibold rounded-full border border-transparent text-black hover:text-gray-600 disabled:opacity-50 disabled:pointer-events-none dark:text-white dark:hover:text-neutral-400" href="mailto:tworabbitrescue@yahoo.com">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="flex-shrink-0 size-5"><rect width="20" height="16" x="2" y="4" rx="2"/><path d="m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7"/></svg>
				</a>
				</div>
				<!-- End Social Brands -->
			</div>
			<!-- End Grid -->
			</div>
		</footer>
		<!-- ========== END FOOTER ========== -->


		<!-- JS Implementing Plugins -->

		<!-- JS PLUGINS -->
		<!-- Required plugins -->
		<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/preline/dist/preline.min.js"></script>
	</main>
</Layout>
